item.dc:creator: @runefreak10 runefreak10
item.description:
@runefreak10 wrote:

If it’s a censor for the public chat, then it would be located in packet 4 (case 4:) in the client class. If you don’t see anything in there, then just search for one of the words it censors in the client class. Otherwise, it has to do with your client, which is what I’m willing to bet.
